# Create identity, verify, drop, verify gone

admin 'CREATE USER ephemeral_user'
replicate
---
version: 2

query 'FROM system::identities FILTER {name == "ephemeral_user"} MAP {name: name, enabled: enabled}'
---
+------------------+-----------+
|       name       |  enabled  |
+------------------+-----------+
|  ephemeral_user  |   true    |
+------------------+-----------+

admin 'DROP USER ephemeral_user'
replicate
---
version: 3

query 'FROM system::identities FILTER {name == "ephemeral_user"} MAP {name: name, enabled: enabled}'
---
+--------+-----------+
|  name  |  enabled  |
+--------+-----------+
+--------+-----------+
